# backtest-ape

Backtesting and forward-testing (via Monte Carlo sims) for DeFi strategies.

## Installation

```sh
hatch build
hatch shell
(backtest-ape) $ ape plugins install .
```

## Build

```sh
(backtest-ape) $ ape compile --size
```

## Test

```sh
(backtest-ape) $ ape test -s
```

## Usage

```sh
(backtest-ape) $ ape run backtester
